  <summary date="2024-03-18T18:05:16Z" status="Introduced in House">Nationwide Right To Unionize Act

This bill authorizes labor agreements to require membership in a labor organization (i.e., union) as a condition of employment regardless of state law (thus preempting any state laws that prohibit such agreements).</summary>
